telemetry.event.game_load_times.descript: Tsyy shyhjiann huey tsehliang youshih chiidonq gehgeh jieduann .de shyrcharng yii bangjuh woo.mhen jaodaw youshih chiidonq .de shinqneng iouhuah dean.
telemetry.event.game_load_times.title: Youshih jiatzay shyrjian
telemetry.event.performance_metrics.desc:
Leaujiee Minecraft .de jeengtii shinqneng gaykuanq, keeyii bangjuh woo.mhen jenduey gehjoong jishyng her tsautzuohshihtoong tyaujeeng yeu iouhuah youshih. 
Youshih baanbeenshinnshi yee bauharn tzay chyijong, yii bangjuh woo.mhen biijiaw Minecraft shin baanbeen .de shinqneng gaykuanq.
telemetry.event.world_load_times.descrip: Duey woo.mhen erlyan, leaujiee jiaruh shyhjieh suoo shiu .de shyrcharng, yiijyi jeh ishyr jaang swei.je shyrjiantueiyi huey ruher biannhuah shyh heen jonqyaw .de.biiru, dang woo.mhen jiaruh shin gongneng huoh jinnshyng jiawdah .de jihshuh genggae shyr, woo.mhen shiuyaw jydaw jeh duey jiatzay shyrjian yeouher yiingsheang.
telemetry.event.world_load_times.title: Shyhjieh jiatzay shyrjian
telemetry.event.world_loaded.description:
Leaujiee wanjia wan Minecraft shyr .de shihjye (lihru youshih moshyh、kehhuhduan huoh fwuwuhduan shyhfoou bey shiougae, yiijyi youshih baanbeen) yeoujuhyu woo.mhen tzay youshih gengshin shyr juhjonq gaejinn wanjia tzuey guanshin .de buh.fen. 
Shyhjieh jiatzay shyhjiann jiang torng shyhjieh shiehtzay shyhjiann ichii yonqyu jihsuann youshih hueyhuah .de chyrshiuh shyr jaang.
telemetry.event.world_loaded.title: Shyhjieh jiatzay
telemetry.event.world_unloaded.descripti:
Tsyy shyhjiann yeu shyhjieh jiatzay shyhjiann yonqyu jihsuann shyhjieh hueyhuah .de chyrshiuhshyrjian. 
Chyrshiuhshyrjian (yii meau her keh wey danwey) tzay shyhjieh hueyhuah jyeshuh shyr (tueyhwei daw biautyi pyngmuh, huoh tsorng fwuwuhchih duannkailianjie) tsehliang.
